<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ب ض ع<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٦٤٩ - ب ض ع]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>بضَّعَ يبضِّع، تَبْضيعًا، فهو مُبضِّع، والمفعول مُبضَّع<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• بضَّعَ الفاكهةَ:</span> أبضعها، جعلها بِضَاعة.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• بضَّع اللَّحْمَ:</span> بضَعه، قطعه <span class="c1">"بضَّع الجلدَ: شقَّه"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">• بضَّع الجثَّةَ:</span> شرَّحها.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>